  "tests": [
    {
      "text": "<p>Trebalo bi da imaš element <code>a</code> direktno pre <code>label</code> sa tekstom <code>Read our terms and conditions</code>.</p>",
      "testString": "assert.match(document.querySelector('fieldset:nth-child(3) + a')?.innerText.trim().replaceAll(/\\s+/g, ' '), /Read our terms and conditions\\.?/i);"
    },
    {
      "text": "<p>Funkcija <code>a</code> bi trebalo da ima <code>href</code> od <code>https://www.freecodecamp.org/news/terms-of-service/</code>.</p>",
      "testString": "assert.match(document.querySelector('fieldset:nth-child(3) + a')?.href, /https:\\/\\/www\\.freecodecamp\\.org\\/news\\/terms-of-service\\/?/);"
    },
    {
      "text": "<p>Trebalo bi da imaš element <code>input</code> unutar <code>label</code>.</p>",
      "testString": "assert.exists(document.querySelector('fieldset:nth-child(3) + a + label > input'));"
    },
    {
      "text": "<p>Unutar <code>label</code>, odmah nakon elementa <code>input</code>, treba da ima tekst <code>I accept the terms and conditions</code>.</p>",
      "testString": "assert.include(document.querySelector('fieldset:nth-child(3) + a + label')?.textContent.trim().replaceAll(/\\s+/g, ' '), 'I accept the terms and conditions');"
    }
  ],
  "description": "<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Dodajte ankerski element sa tekstom <code>Read our terms and conditions</code> pre <code>label</code>, koji je nedavno dodan. Postavite <code>href</code> na:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-md\">https://www.freecodecamp.org/news/terms-of-service/\n</code></pre>\n<p>Zatim dodajte tekst <code>I accept the terms and conditions</code> jednom nakon polja za unos u oznaku.</p>\n</section>",
